org.eclipse.viatra.cep.core.engine.compiler

Class MappingPatterns

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.impl.BaseQueryGroup
      • org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.impl.BaseGeneratedPatternGroup
        • org.eclipse.viatra.cep.core.engine.compiler.MappingPatterns
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.IQueryGroup

    public final class MappingPatterns
extends org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.impl.BaseGeneratedPatternGroup
    A pattern group formed of all patterns defined in mappingPatterns.vql.

    Use the static instance as any org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.IPatternGroup, to conveniently prepare a VIATRA Query engine for matching all patterns originally defined in file mappingPatterns.vql, in order to achieve better performance than one-by-one on-demand matcher initialization.

    From package org.eclipse.viatra.cep.core.engine.compiler, the group contains the definition of the following patterns:

    • translatedEventPattern
    • atomicEventPattern
    • complexPattern
    • followsPattern
    • orPattern
    • andPattern
    • notPattern
    • complexTransition
    • negativeTransition
    • complexFollowsTransition
    • complexOrTransition
    • complexAndTransition
    • nonUnfoldedNotTransition
    • complexNotTransition
    See Also:
    IPatternGroup
